<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddc8d091e-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee" identifier="/us/usc/t2/s168a"><num value="168a">§ 168a.</num><heading> Printing of Constitution Annotated as Senate documents</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">All hardbound revised editions and all cumulative pocket-part supplements shall be printed as Senate documents.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="iddc8d091f-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee">(<ref href="/us/pl/91/589/s2">Pub. L. 91–589, § 2</ref>, <date date="1970-12-24">Dec. 24, 1970</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/84/1586">84 Stat. 1586</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
